WHAT'S NEW
==========

This is the initial creation of agEventPackage.  It's current functionality includes:

- Allows Scenarios to be deployed as Events
- Communicates with agClient to record client records


SYSTEM REQUIREMENTS
===================

*** IMPORTANT NOTE: ***

The agFooPackage plugin is the template plugin for Agasti Mayon development and does not currently enhance functionality.  To enable this plugin Sahana Agasti 2.0 must be installed.

Enter any specific Sys Requirements for agEventPackage.


